name: digiBlossom01
description: digiBlossoms (spring collection variant 2 of 12): this project is an exercise in proceduralism - a recipe is developed for the creation of digital blossoms. These iterations have been informed by social media requests with the following characteristics: A colour, a number or 2, and an adjective pertaining to dimension. If you are interested in acquiring a personal blossom for you garden, please get in touch: info@egmontas.xyz | @egmontas
